{"tid":2367363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"煲底非法集結案 高級督察龍俊胤庭上供稱案發時認不到被捕者樣貌","createTime":"2021-01-15T09:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T12:25:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c68b5cda1a9094dbf7f97ce6e32f12163eacd83f","tid":2367363,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:35:55.000Z","msg":"103萬名市民於前年6月9日參與反修例大遊行，惟政府當日深夜仍回應指送中惡法將如期直上立法會二讀，惹來大批市民於翌日凌晨在立會「煲底」聚集，並與警方發生衝突，多人事後被控非法集結及阻差辦公罪，案件今續審。當日有份追捕示威者的高級督察今在裁判官鄧少雄要求下，於庭上認人，惟督察看過被告脫下口罩的外貌後稱：「我當時睇唔到佢個樣。」<br />\n<br />\n隸屬機動部隊總部的高級督察龍俊胤供稱，前年6月10日深夜12時許到達立法會示威區增援，看見約200名暴力群眾衝擊警方防線，當中有人投擲水樽及雨傘等硬物。<br />\n<br />\n其間龍發現一名身穿白色上衣人士向警方防線掟水樽，於是上前將他捉住，惟對方極力掙扎，同時有身穿綠衫灰褲的人拉住龍的手，結果白衣人士成功逃脫。龍隨即將綠衣人按在地上制服，並由同袍帶那人到警方防線後方。<br />\n<br />\n雖然庭上透露控辯雙方均不爭議被龍的同袍拘捕之綠衣人，就是被告電腦技術員，但裁判官鄧少雄仍要求被告脫下口罩，讓龍辨認涉案人士是否被告。不過龍看過溫的外貌後供稱：「我當時睇唔到佢個樣。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/3BUSPUWW7ZA7NGWEFACTEPTZEA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2F3BUSPUWW7ZA7NGWEFACTEPTZEA%2F&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFmINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=8a4778ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2F3BUSPUWW7ZA7NGWEFACTEPTZEA%2F&h=59df9f07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/3BUSPUWW7ZA7NGWEFACTEPTZEA/</a>"},{"pid":"2db6ed9c1ecb492ad6c7979162411cee4fb2cf87","tid":2367363,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9227fa2f34793db988d3bf2b82cfc02e88add91","tid":2367363,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:40:39.000Z","msg":"其實我唔太明<br />\n既然個官都叫得被告拉低口罩<br />\n個黑警點解唔會係唔係都話認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9741b90faf730ecc11307f68bf44e1ae791d1833","tid":2367363,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:42:29.000Z","msg":"我唔係好明點解要係連登出呢個POST囉"},{"pid":"094386bba081ef8e69174ba149de80daf1053fd8","tid":2367363,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9227fa2f34793db988d3bf2b82cfc02e88add91","tid":2367363,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:40:39.000Z","msg":"其實我唔太明<br />\n既然個官都叫得被告拉低口罩<br />\n個黑警點解唔會係唔係都話認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:42:57.000Z","msg":"如果辯方知道佢唔認得個人懶醒盤問時一定會chur鳩佢<br />\n打到佢唔係誠實可靠證人"},{"pid":"80978b34bd61e0e2c5e1c615a393c97e776bbaf4","tid":2367363,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439848fefb1697690afca3d9b2541204bb5a7646","tid":2367363,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}